---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { companyName } from '../../content/site';
---

<Layout
  locale="en"
  title={`Privacy | ${companyName}`}
  description="Privacy policy for the BenchTrust pre-launch landing page."
  path="/en/privacy/"
  alternatePath="/datenschutz/"
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24 text-slate-200 md:px-10">
    <div class="panel-surface rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-300/80">BenchTrust GmbH</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-base leading-8 text-slate-300">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">1. Privacy at a glance</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">We take the protection of your personal data very seriously. When you use our pre-launch website (prelaunch.benchtrust.com) and sign up for our waitlist, various personal data is collected. This privacy policy explains what data we collect, what we use it for and on what legal basis.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">2. Controller</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Data processing on this website is carried out by the website operator:</p>
          <p class="mt-2">BenchTrust GmbH<br />Lange Strasse 75, 76530 Baden-Baden, Germany<br />Email: contact@benchtrust.com</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">3. Data collection on our website (the waitlist)</h2>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Type of data:</strong> When you sign up for our early access / waitlist, we collect your name, business email address and your stated role (buyer or provider).</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Purpose:</strong> We use this data exclusively to inform you about the launch of our platform on 1 July 2026, to grant you early access ("sneak peeks") and to prepare your future profile accurately.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Legal basis:</strong> Processing of this data is based on your consent (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR). You may withdraw your consent at any time (e.g. by clicking "Unsubscribe" in our emails or by emailing us). The lawfulness of processing carried out before the withdrawal remains unaffected.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">4. Waitlist management (self-hosted, double opt-in)</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">The Co-Creator waitlist is managed entirely in-house – we do <strong>not</strong> use an external CRM or marketing tool such as HubSpot.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Process:</strong> When you submit the form, your input (name, email, role, optional feedback) is embedded into a cryptographically signed confirmation link that is sent to you by email. Only by clicking this link do you actively confirm your sign-up (double opt-in under the GDPR).</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Storage:</strong> For the pre-launch phase we operate <strong>no</strong> database. We do not persistently store your data on our systems. After successful confirmation you receive a welcome email with access to the Co-Creator Lab and an internal notification is sent to our founding team. Confirmation links expire after 72 hours.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-white">Processors:</strong> Email delivery involves the following service providers: <em>Vercel Inc.</em> (function hosting, see section&nbsp;5) and <em>IONOS SE</em>, Elgendorfer Straße 57, 56410 Montabaur, Germany (mailbox and SMTP delivery). Appropriate data processing agreements are in place.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">5. Hosting (Vercel)</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Our static pre-launch website is hosted by Vercel Inc. When you visit our site, the host automatically collects technical connection data (e.g. IP address, browser type, time) to deliver the page reliably and securely (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR).</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">6. Your rights</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">You have the right at any time to obtain free information about the origin, recipients and purpose of your stored personal data. You also have the right to request the correction, blocking or deletion of this data. Please contact us at the address stated above.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <a class="mt-10 inline-flex rounded-full border border-white/15 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-cyan-300/60 hover:text-cyan-200" href="/">
        Back to homepage
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>